### *straglr*, for CAG count

CL Merge 100 bam:

```bash
for n in $(seq 13 19) ; do bash ~/straglr/jobs/bash-merge_100_BAM.sh /lustrehome/gianluca/cattaneo/data/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3/20220913_1818_MN38445_FAT23748_d8b5cadc/analysis/alignment/barcode${n}_WG ; done
```

CL Job submission:

```bash
mkdir /lustrehome/gianluca/straglr/output/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3

cd /lustrehome/gianluca/cattaneo/data/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3/20220913_1818_MN38445_FAT23748_d8b5cadc/analysis/alignment/

for n in $(seq 13 19) ; do ls barcode${n}_WG/*.multi.bam | while IFS="$(printf '/')" read -r f1 f2 ; do echo condor_submit -name ettore \
-a "out_dir=/lustrehome/gianluca/straglr/output/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3/" \
-a "bam=/lustrehome/gianluca/cattaneo/data/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3/20220913_1818_MN38445_FAT23748_d8b5cadc/analysis/alignment/barcode${n}_WG/${f2}" \
-a "ref=/lustre/home/enza/cattaneo/data/Methylation-RUES2-FLG/RUES2-20CAG/reference/GCA_000001405.15_GRCh38_no_alt_analysis_set.fna" \
-a "out_prefix=barcode${n}_v4_${f2}" \
-a "bed=/lustrehome/gianluca/test_straglr/CAG_v4.bed" \
-a "file=${f2}" \
-a "barcode=barcode${n}" \
/lustrehome/gianluca/straglr/jobs/condor-straglr_exp.job ; done ; done | less -S
```

### Merge multiple *straglr* output - version CAG_v4.bed

```bash
cd /lustrehome/gianluca/straglr/output/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_NANOPORE2-3

for n in $(seq 13 19) ; do ls barcode${n}_v4_split*.tsv | grep aa | while read file ; do cat ${file} > barcode${n}_v4.tsv; done ; done

for n in $(seq 13 19) ; do ls barcode${n}_v4_split*.tsv | grep -v aa | while read file ; do cat ${file} | grep -v "#" >> barcode${n}_v4.tsv; done ; done

#cancel all .ok files created for job-control
rm *.ok
```

### LHA 19 CAG allele

```bash

DATA=/lustrehome/gianluca/consensus_fetus/20220930_test
FILE_F=readID_forward_barcode07_19cag.txt
FILE_R=readID_reverse_barcode07_19cag.txt
OUTPUT=barcode07_19cag_consensus.fa
OUTPUT_FOLDER=barcode07_19cag

cat ${DATA}/${FILE_F} | head -n 500 > ${DATA}/readID_forward.txt 
cat ${DATA}/${FILE_R} | head -n 500 > ${DATA}/readID_reverse.txt 

/lustrehome/gianluca/.conda/envs/artic_ncov/bin/./seqkit grep -f ${DATA}/readID_forward.txt  ~/cattaneo/data/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_LHA/20220913_1732_MN37986_FAT23850_f89f2b41/analysis/fastq2fasta/barcode07_allreads.fasta -o ${DATA}/readID_forward_1.fa
/lustrehome/gianluca/.conda/envs/artic_ncov/bin/./seqkit grep -f ${DATA}/readID_reverse.txt  ~/cattaneo/data/AC2021_NANOPORE_PCR10/1_2_3_4_6_8_HD_LHA/20220913_1732_MN37986_FAT23850_f89f2b41/analysis/fastq2fasta/barcode07_allreads.fasta -o ${DATA}/readID_reverse.fa

/lustrehome/gianluca/github/seqtk/./seqtk seq -r ${DATA}/readID_reverse.fa > ${DATA}/readID_forward_2.fa

cat ${DATA}/readID_forward_1.fa ${DATA}/readID_forward_2.fa > ${DATA}/readID_forward_3.fa

/lustrehome/gianluca/github/spoa/build/bin/./spoa -r 0 -s -l 1 ${DATA}/readID_forward_3.fa > ${DATA}/${OUTPUT}

~/.conda/envs/medaka/bin/./medaka_consensus -i ${DATA}/readID_forward_3.fa -d ${DATA}/${OUTPUT} -o ${DATA}/${OUTPUT_FOLDER}
```
